      <title>加纳启动 5.3​​2 亿美元计划，助力危机后企业发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/ghana-starts-532-million-plan-to-bolster-companies-after-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在债务重组影响到企业增长之后，加纳启动了一项举措来支持其中小企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/ghana-starts-532-million-plan-to-bolster-companies-after-crisis</guid>
