    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织警告称莫桑比克将裁减 5,000 名“幽灵工人”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/mozambique-to-cut-5-000-ghost-workers-imf-says-after-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，莫桑比克将在本月底前从其工资单上剔除至少 5,000 名所谓的“幽灵工人”，此前国际货币基金组织曾就莫桑比克不断膨胀的公共工资支出发出警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/mozambique-to-cut-5-000-ghost-workers-imf-says-after-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家表示支持对中国电动汽车征收临时关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/eu-nations-signal-support-for-provisional-tariffs-on-china-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，欧盟成员国在一次不具约束力的秘密投票中表示支持对从中国出口的电动汽车征收临时关税，这表明欧盟有意在贸易问题上与世界第二大经济体较量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/eu-nations-signal-support-for-provisional-tariffs-on-china-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:15:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对中国电动汽车进口征收关税后英国考虑作出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/uk-weighs-response-after-eu-imposes-tariffs-on-china-ev-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟宣布对从中国进口的电动汽车征收临时关税后，英国政府表示“担心”电动汽车进口的影响，并考虑采取可能的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/uk-weighs-response-after-eu-imposes-tariffs-on-china-ev-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:10:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西总统卢拉计划放弃投资者寻求的结构性支出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/brazil-s-lula-plans-to-forgo-structural-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的财政目标实现计划必定会让那些期待结构性削减开支的人们感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/brazil-s-lula-plans-to-forgo-structural-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:56:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和欧盟国家制定计划应对俄罗斯干预美国选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/uk-eu-states-plan-response-to-election-interference-by-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和其他欧洲国家计划在本周举行的欧洲政治共同体会议上揭露俄罗斯虚假信息的新例子，以对克里姆林宫涉嫌干涉西方选举做出更为强硬的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/uk-eu-states-plan-response-to-election-interference-by-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普副总统人选加剧欧洲对美国支持基辅的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-fuels-european-anxiety-over-us-backing-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年慕尼黑安全会议上，当一位愤怒的乌克兰议员斥责 JD Vance 指责共和党阻止向乌克兰提供援助时，这位美国参议员耐心地听着。但 Oleksiy Honcharenko 却无法改变他的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-fuels-european-anxiety-over-us-backing-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
